{
  "stem": "10862.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever you had to take showers, they were cold water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was no soap.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it had a horrible odors, just awful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I can remember is the lice and the bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, all I could-- when I'm sitting here now in my beautiful, clean home, I can just visualize how horrible it was-- you know, the lice and the bed bugs, and all the other roaches, whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had no shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had-- my feet were wrapped with rags.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I said, it was very, very cold, and your feet were chapped, and your hands were chapped, and you had these wounds from, from just the cold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very, very painful-- very painful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think in our barrack they must have hit 100 women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure, but I would think there must have been about 100 because they had layers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we had three-- one barrack on top of the-- not barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are those called?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bunks-- bunks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think there were like, three, three bunks at a time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were together, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always slept together in the same barr-- in the same bunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we sort of kept ourselves warm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of them talked about their families that they had lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them had come from Hungary, people from different parts of Europe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they talked about their loved ones that they had lost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lost their wives-- I mean mothers, brothers, husbands, most of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they thought, when is it all going to end?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why do we have to suffer like this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why doesn't come-- somebody come along and save us?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, everybody has deserted us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For what reason?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why is this necessary?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
